<p><strong data-path-to-node="6,6,0" data-index-in-node="0">Mobile:</strong> 07999 123321</p>
<p><strong data-path-to-node="6,6,0" data-index-in-node="21">IF WE CAN’T FIX IT, IT CAN’T BE FIXED!</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="0">B. ROD’S CAR HIRE</strong></span></p>
